  "text": "Notice that the mid-point method (28) is implicit, and is a symplectic method for stochastic Hamiltonian systems which automatically preserves quadratic conversed quantity [CITATION_1] . Now applying the mid-point method (28) as the supporting method in the projection method, and using the property of a kind of discrete gradient∇I(x,X):",
